(
  'Kingdom Centre Tower: Everything You Need to Know',
  'kingdom-centre-tower-everything-you-need-to-know',
  'Complete guide to Kingdom Centre Tower in Riyadh — the Sky Bridge observation deck, mall, ticket prices, opening hours, and how to get there.',
  '<img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1591604129939-f1efa4d9f7fa?w=900&q=80" alt="Kingdom Centre Tower Riyadh skyline" style="width:100%;border-radius:16px;margin-bottom:24px;max-height:400px;object-fit:cover;"/>
<h2>Kingdom Centre Tower: Everything You Need to Know</h2>
<p>Instantly recognisable by its inverted-arch "bottle opener" silhouette, Kingdom Centre Tower is one of Riyadh''s most iconic landmarks. At 302 metres, it dominates the Olaya skyline, and the Sky Bridge connecting its two peaks offers the best panoramic view in the city.</p>
