<tr><td style="padding:10px;border-bottom:1px solid #e2e8f0;">Level 4 (Ladies Kingdom)</td><td style="padding:10px;border-bottom:1px solid #e2e8f0;">Women-only floor with boutiques and a gym</td></tr>
