<h2>How to Get There</h2><p>Kingdom Centre Tower sits on King Fahd Road in the Olaya district, central to most of Riyadh''s business hotels. <strong>Airport Travel Taxis</strong> offers fixed-price transfers from King Khalid International Airport and all Riyadh hotels. <a href="/booking">Book your transfer</a></p>',
