<h2>Boulevard Riyadh City: A Complete Visitor Guide</h2>
<p>Boulevard Riyadh City is the capital''s flagship lifestyle and entertainment destination, split into two zones — Boulevard World and Boulevard City — packed with restaurants, live shows, funfair rides, and seasonal pop-up experiences that anchor much of the annual Riyadh Season programme.</p>
