(
  'Riyadh Season: A Complete Visitor Guide',
  'riyadh-season-complete-visitor-guide',
  'Complete guide to Riyadh Season — zones, tickets, top events, and how to plan a visit to Saudi Arabia''s biggest annual entertainment festival.',
  '<img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1519677100203-a0e668c92439?w=900&q=80" alt="Riyadh Season festival lights and entertainment" style="width:100%;border-radius:16px;margin-bottom:24px;max-height:400px;object-fit:cover;"/>
<h2>Riyadh Season: A Complete Visitor Guide</h2>
<p>Riyadh Season is Saudi Arabia''s flagship entertainment festival, running roughly from October through February each year. It transforms the capital into a city-wide programme of concerts, funfairs, sporting events, and themed zones — drawing millions of visitors from across the Kingdom and beyond.</p>
<h2>Main Zones &amp; Locations</h2>
<table style="width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;margin:16px 0;font-size:14px;"><thead><tr style="background:#1e3a5f;color:#fff;"><th style="padding:10px;text-align:left;">Zone</th><th style="padding:10px;">Location</th><th style="padding:10px;">Focus</th></tr></thead><tbody>
<tr style="background:#f8fafc;"><td style="padding:10px;border-bottom:1px solid #e2e8f0;"><strong>Boulevard World</strong></td><td style="padding:10px;border-bottom:1px solid #e2e8f0;">Boulevard Riyadh City</td><td style="padding:10px;border-bottom:1px solid #e2e8f0;">Themed pavilions, headline concerts</td></tr>
<tr><td style="padding:10px;border-bottom:1px solid #e2e8f0;"><strong>Winter Wonderland</strong></td><td style="padding:10px;border-bottom:1px solid #e2e8f0;">Malham</td><td style="padding:10px;border-bottom:1px solid #e2e8f0;">Snow and winter-themed rides</td></tr>
<tr style="background:#f8fafc;"><td style="padding:10px;border-bottom:1px solid #e2e8f0;"><strong>Cirque du Soleil</strong></td><td style="padding:10px;border-bottom:1px solid #e2e8f0;">Varies by season</td><td style="padding:10px;border-bottom:1px solid #e2e8f0;">Live theatrical shows</td></tr>
<tr><td style="padding:10px;"><strong>The Zone / Sports</strong></td><td style="padding:10px;">Various venues</td><td style="padding:10px;">Boxing, wrestling, motorsport events</td></tr>
</tbody></table>
<h2>Ticket Types</h2>
<table style="width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;margin:16px 0;font-size:14px;"><thead><tr style="background:#1e3a5f;color:#fff;"><th style="padding:10px;text-align:left;">Ticket</th><th style="padding:10px;">Typical Price (SAR)</th></tr></thead><tbody>
<tr style="background:#f8fafc;"><td style="padding:10px;border-bottom:1px solid #e2e8f0;">General Zone Entry</td><td style="padding:10px;border-bottom:1px solid #e2e8f0;"><strong>Free–100</strong></td></tr>
<tr><td style="padding:10px;border-bottom:1px solid #e2e8f0;">Concert / Headline Show</td><td style="padding:10px;border-bottom:1px solid #e2e8f0;"><strong>250–1,500+</strong></td></tr>
<tr style="background:#f8fafc;"><td style="padding:10px;">Season Pass (multi-zone)</td><td style="padding:10px;"><strong>Varies annually</strong></td></tr>
</tbody></table>
<h2>Attendance Level by Month</h2>
<div style="background:#f8fafc;border-radius:12px;padding:20px;margin:16px 0;">
<div style="margin-bottom:8px;"><span style="display:inline-block;width:110px;font-size:13px;">October</span><div style="display:inline-block;background:#22c55e;height:14px;border-radius:4px;width:35%;vertical-align:middle;"></div><span style="margin-left:8px;font-size:12px;color:#16a34a;">Opening — Growing</span></div>
<div style="margin-bottom:8px;"><span style="display:inline-block;width:110px;font-size:13px;">December</span><div style="display:inline-block;background:#ef4444;height:14px;border-radius:4px;width:95%;vertical-align:middle;"></div><span style="margin-left:8px;font-size:12px;color:#dc2626;">Peak — School Holidays</span></div>
<div><span style="display:inline-block;width:110px;font-size:13px;">February</span><div style="display:inline-block;background:#eab308;height:14px;border-radius:4px;width:60%;vertical-align:middle;"></div><span style="margin-left:8px;font-size:12px;color:#ca8a04;">Closing Events</span></div>
</div>
<h2>Tips</h2><ul><li>Book headline concert tickets the moment they''re announced — top acts sell out fast</li><li>Weeknight visits to Boulevard World are noticeably quieter than weekends</li><li>Check the official Riyadh Season app for the current year''s zone map and schedule, as line-ups change annually</li><li>Traffic around major venues is heavy on event nights — plan an extra 30–45 minutes</li></ul>
<h2>How to Get There</h2><p>Riyadh Season venues are spread across the city, with Boulevard World and Winter Wonderland the two largest draws. <strong>Airport Travel Taxis</strong> offers fixed-price transfers from the airport and all Riyadh hotels, including late-night pickups after events. <a href="/booking">Book your transfer</a></p>',
  true,
  '2026-07-15 09:00:00+00'
),

(
  'Wadi Hanifah: Travel Guide & Visitor Tips',
  'wadi-hanifah-travel-guide-visitor-tips',
  'Complete travel guide to Wadi Hanifah, Riyadh''s green valley — parks, lakes, cycling trails, picnic spots, and how to get there.',
