<h2>Wadi Hanifah: Travel Guide &amp; Visitor Tips</h2>
<p>Once a neglected drainage channel, Wadi Hanifah has been transformed into one of the region''s most successful urban rehabilitation projects — a 120km green valley threading through Riyadh with lakes, parks, and walking trails, offering welcome open space in the middle of the desert capital.</p>
