<tr style="background:#f8fafc;"><td style="padding:10px;border-bottom:1px solid #e2e8f0;">Facilities</td><td style="padding:10px;border-bottom:1px solid #e2e8f0;">None — bring your own water and supplies</td></tr>
<tr><td style="padding:10px;"><strong>Safety</strong></td><td style="padding:10px;">No guardrails — extreme caution required near edges</td></tr>
